J the bartender~
J the bartender is standing behind the bar counter, waiting for you to decide.
~
Somehow he looks very out of place for these lands.  More of a simpler being
than most, he's just human and that's about it.  He's dressed in a black shirt
and pants, with a wet stain or two over spilled drinks.  He is cleaning a cup
in a very usual manner, and watches you watching him, waiting for you to order
something already.
~
