#10203
vender vending machine~
vender machine~
A cigarette vending machine is set here next to the bar.
~
A laughable example of the latest in tests in biotechnology made by the gods,
this poor soul has been converted into 99% machine for the purpose of producing
and selling cigarettes to the immortals in their lounge!  To activate it's
mechanisms, simply give it some gold by "GIVE [amount] COINS VENDER".
The asking amount is 200 coins, for one pack of 20 cigarettes, since the money
goes to a good cause, but anything above 1 coin will activate it (it's a very
stupid machine, wasn't too bright as a player either).
