#ROOMS
#10201
Garren & Associates~
You stand in the medium sized, one room office.  It's not incredibly large, but
serves it's purpose.  There is a single desk in the middle of the room, towards
the north wall, with a large black office chair standing out from behind it.
Miscellaneous papers are scattered across it's top, as well as on top of
several tall cabinets which line the western side of the room, each made of a
simple metal and supporting three large drawers for the owner to log his
many files into.  To the north as well, behind the desk and chair, is a window
leading out somewhere into the world.
~
~
